narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Continuation of L3. Less emphasis on the grammar/textbook learning and more discussion of movies, readings etc. Good class.

Italian four is a class that goes over the more advanced grammar while giving you a cultural overview of some of the the more prominent facts about italian culture. I would advise this level because you finish the year know all the grammar you can learn about italian.
Yes, I would recommend this class given that you have completed the first three levels.
